Package: linux-image-6.18-sky1
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, kmod, linux-base
Recommends: linux-headers-6.18-sky1, sky1-firmware
Description: Linux kernel image for CIX Sky1 SoC
 Linux kernel 6.18 LTS with patches for CIX Sky1 SoC support including:
  - Panthor GPU driver (Mali-G720)
  - Display drivers (linlon-dp, trilin-dpsub)
  - PCIe, USB, audio subsystems
  - Power management and thermal
 .
 This package contains the kernel image and modules.

Package: linux-headers-6.18-sky1
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux kernel headers for CIX Sky1 SoC
 This package provides the kernel headers for linux-image-6.18-sky1.
 Required for building out-of-tree kernel modules (DKMS).

Package: linux-dtbs-6.18-sky1
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Device tree blobs for CIX Sky1 boards
 This package contains the compiled device tree blobs (DTBs) for:
  - CIX Sky1 SoC (sky1.dtsi)
  - Radxa Orion O6 board (sky1-orion-o6.dtb)
